{"tid":1638780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國終於有反應，但我好怕大家會靜左落黎","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T05:18:50.000Z","uid":36797,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b025f87b3a87e74dc88e1e1276bcee7686003a","tid":1638780,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"各區開花，除左少左勇武手足比人拉，黑警淨係可以鳩拉街坊，仲見到樣野好開心，就係多左中年街坊一直屌鳩班差佬，終於聚到更多真香港人一齊行。<br />\n<br />\n我希望各區會繼續，因為仲有好多未有交代既懸案，生死未卜既兄弟，受逼害既香港人受緊苦。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好自滿，唔好自我膨脹&hellip;唔好喺依個緊張既時候做錯事，一定要謹慎，冷靜，堅持，Be humble。<br />\n當港共被逼到入窮巷，手段只會更加殘忍，更加恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"dea80009bd3886e365fdda6858946ad53d186736","tid":1638780,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6871dfb994a1fbb730a2baa361c0e1f5c621b5","tid":1638780,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fea618ea8ead6c0ec14ca35027416f934e5f69d","tid":1638780,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bab641eb8b280c9cd937588d312ba21d6e169cf","tid":1638780,"uid":285899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"多區開花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陣地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb12e4d9971ac2ef5dfeb6441d3d9a0c1931857","tid":1638780,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"三日前講<br />\n今日唔洗驚啦 真係發生左"},{"pid":"cd3ae373e8d0fe6fb821d33019e29041e2602603","tid":1638780,"uid":204039,"like":0,"dis